OL,6,FRecalling the incident, the personal
OL,7,Ftrainer told ITV News London: "(It was
OL,8,Fthe) biggest spider I've ever seen
OL,9,Fwith my own eyes - scurried up from
OL,10,Funderneath my elbow, up my forum onto
OL,11,Fthe top of my hand.
OL,13,F"It stared me in the eyes, as if to
OL,14,Fsay, get ready and stuck his fangs in
OL,15,Fit was in slow motion.
OL,17,F"And then that felt like a soldering
OL,18,Firon stuck into my hand."
