OL,3,CMan almost lost arm and was '12 hours
OL,4,Cfrom death' after spider bite
OL,6,FSoon after, he felt very unwell and
OL,7,Fmanaged to call the emergency services
OL,8,Fbefore collapsing.
OL,10,FHe was rushed to intensive care at
OL,11,FWexham Park Hospital in Slough, where
OL,12,Fhe later developed sepsis.
OL,14,FHe remained unconscious for three days
OL,15,Fand, after he awoke, doctors told him
OL,16,Fhis right hand was almost amputated.
OL,18,FThe medics who saved his hand and his
OL,19,Flife also told the former personal
OL,20,Ftrainer he was just 12 hours from
OL,21,Fdeath.
